<sn><md>**Day 2 – Same Pharmacy, Another Chemist (Chemist1)**

---

- **Emon:** Hi, I was here yesterday for Rolack, but I got this medicine instead. Can I exchange it for Rolack?

- **Chemist1:** Oh, I’m **Chemist1**. Let me check… So you want **Rolack**, the painkiller?

- **Emon:** Yes, please. I really needed a proper painkiller.

- **Chemist1:** No problem. Here’s the Rolack. Just take one tablet after food.

- **Emon:** Thank you!

- **Chemist1:** You’re welcome. And next time, mention the exact brand you want, so there’s no mix-up.

- **Emon:** Will do. Thanks again!
